commit.message:
Makefile.in: Regenrate with Automake 1.9.3.

2004-11-24  Kelley Cook  <kcook@gcc.gnu.org>

	* Makefile.in: Regenrate with Automake 1.9.3.
	* aclocal.m4: Likewise.
	* configure: Regenerate.

From-SVN: r91195
